                The project enables users to identify and find the things that they have lost in the past. The project
                is intended to assist VIT students in locating misplaced belongings. It is well known that students
                frequently move from their dormitory to academic buildings without regard to the course of the day.
                <br>
                <br>
                As such, it is common to misplace stuff in the midst of the chaos. Unfortunately, there is no
